derivation: or נָתוּן (Ezra 8:17), (the proper form as passive participle), from H5414 (נָתַן); one given, i.e. (in the plural only)
outline:
1. Nethinims
    1. temple slaves assigned to the Levites and priests for service in the sanctuary
strongs_def: the Nethinim, or Temple-servants (as given to that duty)
